Di temdint-nni n Sars yellan di temdint n Birizi, țelt n Tisirt wway gar-asen ; aṭas n watmaten i gellan di tmura nniḍen, meɛna aṭas n yemdanen i d-yemmeslayen s tutlayt i s-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi, nutni țeffɣen seg-sen imawen-nsen.
Meɛna aṭas n leṣnaf n leqdic i gellan di Ṛebbi akken i t-id-yumeṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, imi i gellan umcafeɛ-agi ț-ținezmarin, axaṭer ayagi d awal n ccariɛa i d-ițasen si tazwara alamma ț-țaggara.
Meɛna s wakka i gesnekmal Sidi Ṛebbi ayen i d-yenna si zik seg imawen n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid n tmurt n Sban.
Dɛut daɣen yal aẓidan n tejmaɛt n iḥeṛṛiyen i d-yusan si tmurt n Kalylan meɛna llant daɣen wid ur nessin ara Sidi Ṛebbi. Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut mliḥ deg waṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, iwakken ad mmeslayen timeslayin ur nețwassen ara, wid nețwassen ara.
Aț-țili d ameqqran n tejmaɛt n ifariziyen ḥemmlen ad yali leqdeṛ, ad sɛunt lḥeṛma d neyya, ad isɛun iman-nsen ;
?ef wannect-agi i gella d amcafeɛ gar-aɣ d Ṛebbi s idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen ad weṛten lxiṛ i sen-iwɛed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Amur nniḍen n zzerriɛa yeɣli ger yedɣaɣen , mi d-temɣi teqquṛ imi xuṣṣen waman.
M'ara d-taseḍ, azeggaɣ daɣen lebxuṛ akk-d leswaṛ n temdint n Lud, azeggaɣ ɣlayen d wayen yețwaxedmen s wedɣaɣ, ur d-țeffɣen seg-s mkul ṣṣenf.
Deg ifragen-agi aṭas n imuḍan i gḍelqen, iderɣalen, iɛibanen d wukrifen țṛaǧun akk ad ḥerrken waman.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, a ț-issers s ufella n lewḥuc :
D ugur ameqqran m'ara ṭṭfen imukan gar-awen ɣer imensi n tegmaț, zehhun mbla lḥecma, țxemmimen kan ɣef yiman-nsen. Cban asigna yețțawi waḍu, ur d-yețțak lehwa ; cban ttjuṛ ur d-nețțak ara lfakya di lawan-nsent, mmutent, qquṛent dɣa țwaqelɛent.
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; ma d nețțat tseddqem-iten, țwagezmen si lehlakat-nsen.
iwakken a d-tbanent licaṛat, ț-țaɛkumt ur nesɛi lfayda, lameɛna a wen-yekkes tacmuxt n tarrawt ur nesɛi lmeɛna, aț-țilim d ugur deg uɛebbuḍ.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Yella yiwen n weɣḍas i yi-țṛaǧun... D leɛtab ameqqran yerna ɣeṣbeɣ melmi ara d-yas wass-nni ! Iwakken i wen-d-yebɛemṛen di lexṣaṣ, lweṛt i cudden-t ɣer iḍaṛṛen n yemnayen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, amenzu n waman ɣef ddunit meṛṛa, llan di leswaq n lebḥeṛ di teṛwiḥt-nni nețwali d llebsa. Llan daɣen wiyaḍ ffren-d leɛṭeṛ n lebḥuṛ, ț-țadmin i d-țwaxedmen s wezṛu.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, d igellil neɣ d azeggaɣ ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf, ur d-yețțak ara daɣen agur neɣ d wayen yellan deg-sen.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Atah wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ tuǧǧal iwakken ur d-yețțili ara wayen ara sent-d-ssukksen.
A nenna-yas d ayen i ɣ-d-isseḍlamen i wul yeṣfan, nessen taktabt-agi n tideț, lameɛna neǧǧu-it-id deg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen.
ur ilaq ara ad țḥessisen i tmucuha n wuɛekkaz, iwakken aț-țwehmem ɣef waṭas n yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna i d-iheddeṛ imeslayen i s-d-yemmeslayen.
Sufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
