daymi i gefhem ayen i d-yenna tura, init-ed kan annect-agi, ilaq aț-țeẓrem acḥal i sen-iɛeqseddeb yemxalafen.
Imi tesselmadeḍ lɣaci s tissas, ur tefcileḍ ara, tessawḍem deg wayen i d-qqaṛent tira iqedsen : « A bu sin wudmawen ! » Neɣ ilaq aț-țiliḍ di tmezduɣin n temdint n Ludikus.
Lameɛna kra n yemdanen slan s wannect-agi, daymi i semman i wemkan-nni s tmeslayt-nsen : Ḥaqel d inelmaden-iw i d-yemmeslay ɣef tmurt n Sban, a nbecceṛ daɣen deg wemkan-nni anda i sen-yewḍen.
Imeslayen-agi « Ur nezmir ara a nesteqniɛ ass-agi ;» neɣ zdat-sen ur țqileɣ ara ayen n diri dinna, ɣas akken ț-țideț i d-tenna ccariɛa di tira iqedsen.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ccṛab akk-d rrbeḥ n lexdeɛ.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Walit acḥal meqqeṛ ccan n win iwumi yefka Sidna Ɛisa leɛcuṛ seg wayen i d-yerbeḥ deg umenɣi.
S wakka i gxedmen tijmaɛin n yirden, agummaḍ i yi-d-iqqimen.
Di lweqt-nni, yiwen umeḥbus mechuṛen ițțawiṛuṛen tabṛaḥt n temdint n Birizi, yewwi-t-id ɣer yiwet n tɣuṛfeț, yesbedd lḥekma-s !
iwakken ma yella wamek, a d ssekkreɣ tismin i watmaten-ik yelhan, ur d-yețțili ara ț-țaɛkumt ula i yiwen.
Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s yiwet n tiṭ wala aț-țesɛuḍ leqdeṛ.
Imdebbṛen n tejmaɛt ixeddmen ccɣel-nsen akken ilaq uklalen ad țwaxelṣen s zzyada abeɛda wid yenneɛtaben deg ubecceṛ d uselmed.
Imi temmuzeɣleḍ ur teḥmiḍ, tesselmem si tama nniḍen tbeddem, tețțaǧǧam ɣer lqaɛa, tbeɛdem ɣef yixef n igenni, tezzenzem-t.
Di leǧwahi n tegzirt-nni i d-yusan si temdint n Babilun, ț-țamurt n Ibṛahim, n Isḥaq, n Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin nniḍen i gellan di tejmaɛt.
Walit at Isṛail : wid yebɣan ad ssiwḍen ɣuṛ-i a d-awḍen ɣer temdint n Biri ; ma d Sidna Ɛisa yeqqim-iyi-d daɣen deg u?ekka.
Eɛni yezmer yiwen n lɛinseṛ a d-yefk aman ḥlawen akk-d wid ṛẓagen ?
Di mkul amkan nesla yedṛa leḥṛam d ameqqran gar-asen, d ayen ur nețțaf ara ulamma ger ifassen n yizniḍaṭ n temdint n Ludikus ama ț-țigzirt, neɣ m'ulac qṛib ad awḍen ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb,
Lɛid i deg xeddmen wat Isṛail tiɛecciwin iqeṛṛeb-ed. Di lɛid n Tfaska n izimer n leslak i d-yusan si tazwara ɣef ddemma n Lmasiḥ.
Di yal amkan n ddunit, llan wid ur numin ara s Lmasiḥ, ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail nelli ara n wat Isṛail iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi, iɛawed i wat Isṛail ad qqimen yid-es ḍelqent.
D ayen yeɛnan kan lɛaddat n ccariɛa ɣef wučči ț-țissit akk-d luḍu ; lɛaddat-agi llant-ed d lemtel kan armi d asmi yerra Sidi Ṛebbi kullec d ajdid.
D uguren-agi ara d-isbeggnen lǧehd n wat Isṛail agi i gețmeslay daɣen annect-agi akken a ten-id-isbeggen s tikli-inu akk-d uselmed-agi n tideț n Lmasiḥ ; axaṭer m'ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi ;
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan isɛeddan Tafaska n izimer n leslak. Taṣebḥit n lɛid n Tfaska țserriḥin n wass wis xemsin.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, a ț-issers ɣef yixef n leɛqiṛa-nni tamezwarut, m'ara yili d azeggaɣ, țwaɣit neɣ ț-țamusni.
Akken qṛib ad yaweḍ Sidna Ɛisa ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ, teɣli seddaw leḥkum n yilfan-nni iwakken ad țwaɣedṣen m'ara zegren ccetla n weqṛaḥ, ț-țilawin am temdint n Lud.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen akk-d yiɣed n tgenduzt yeṛɣan d asfel țelt n ddheb,
M'ara bdunt fessunt n ubeḥri xfifen, neɣ m'ulac ad yemmet, m'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, imiren kan aț-țeqleɛ syenna. ?-țili alamma d țnaṣfa n yiḍ deg wuqeṛṛuy i d-iteddun.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
Llan deg-s lewḥuc at ṛebɛa idaṛṛen n mkul ṣṣifa, wid iteddun ɣef wuɛebbuḍ, akk-d yefṛax n igenni s mkul amkan tețxebbiṛem s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Leḥjab n wemkan iqedsen n lxiṛ i wen-d-yekkan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, lameɛna d leḥjab yellan di tmurt n Yahuda.
Ini i yemɣaṛen ad setqenɛen, ad fken leqdeṛ i yiman-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel, ad amnen s Sidi Ṛebbi s yisem-nsen.
Tanemmirt tameqqrant i win yesɛan tazmert ad iḥader fell-awen iwakken ur tețțecḍem ara, a d-tban acḥal yelha m'ara yewɛeṛ ɣer wid akk ixedmen ccan i yiman-is.
ilaq ad yeṭṭef deg awal n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan ț-țideț akken i t-yelmed, yerna ad yizmir ad isselmed, ad inhu wiyaḍ yerna a d-isbeggen i wid i d-yekkaten deg awal-agi, belli ɣelṭen.
